StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.name: [GetPhysicalFitnessTests]
StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.body:
( @NwaID int ) AS
SET TRANSACTION ISOLATION LEVEL READ UNCOMMITTED
SELECT [ID], [NWAID], [PFTTypeID], [Date], [RunMinutes], [RunSeconds], [Pullups], [Pushups], [Hang.me], [Crunches], [Type] = 'E', [GENDER_CODE] as [Gender], IsPassing, AmmoCanLi., [PlankMinutes], [PlankSeconds], NULL AS AmmoCanLi.Date FROM [USMC].[PhysicalFitnessTest] p. INNER JOIN [dbo].[NWA] n ON p..[NWAID] = n.[NWA_ID] INNER JOIN [dbo].[MARINE_CANDIDATE] mc ON n.[MARINE_CANDIDATE_ID] = mc.[MARINE_CANDIDATE_ID] WHERE [NWAID] = @NwaID
